    <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-12 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">The problem every developer knows</h2>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">!</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">You find the perfect solution</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">That Stack Overflow answer, that brilliant blog post, that GitHub issue that solves your exact problem.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-black text-sm font-bold">⏰</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">You think "I'll bookmark this"</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">But browser bookmarks become a graveyard, and "I'll remember to search for it later" never works.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">?</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Six months later, you need it again</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">You remember the solution exists, but Google only shows you SEO spam and outdated tutorials.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-4 text-violet-600">Pensive fixes this</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Captures full content, not just titles</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Searches through actual article text</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>Works from anywhere: browser, mobile, Telegram</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-violet-600 rounded-full"></div>
                <span>AI-powered summaries and tags</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Getting Started -->
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
