            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI-Powered Insights</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Get automatic summaries and smart tags for every article. AI extracts key insights and organizes your content intelligently.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-violet-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              <span>Automatic article summaries</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-violet-600 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
